flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 75: API Key Lifecycle and Partner Access Control Flow

  Request[Vendor/admin requests API key]
  Approve{Scope request approved?}
  Generate[Generate scoped key]
  Hash[(Store key hash + permissions + rate-limit policy in api_keys)]
  Deliver[Deliver key once]

  Runtime[Partner calls API with key]
  Validate[Validate key hash + status]
  Active{Key active and not revoked?}
  Scope{Requested action within scope?}
  Rate{Within rate limit?}

  Allow[Allow API operation]
  Deny[Deny request]

  Rotate[Rotate key]
  Revoke[Revoke key on compromise]
  Emergency[Emergency revoke and notify owner]

  Request --> Approve
  Approve -- No --> Deny
  Approve -- Yes --> Generate --> Hash --> Deliver --> Runtime

  Runtime --> Validate --> Active
  Active -- No --> Deny
  Active -- Yes --> Scope
  Scope -- No --> Deny
  Scope -- Yes --> Rate
  Rate -- No --> Deny
  Rate -- Yes --> Allow

  Allow --> Rotate --> Runtime
  Validate -->|Compromise signal| Revoke --> Emergency --> Deny
